In the interests of furthering standards for the X Window System,
Adobe Systems Incorporated has contributed to the X Consortium and its
members the Adobe typeface software listed below. This Adobe Type 1
font software donation will now allow users to experience and freely
use traditional high-quality Adobe type in the X Window environment.

The Adobe typefaces (Type 1 font program, bitmaps and Adobe Font
Metric files) donated are:

Utopia Regular
Utopia Italic
Utopia Bold
Utopia Bold Italic

This are the Type1 versions of the Adobe Utopia fonts.
